  description: Increases Attack Speed by 20% and grants 30 Starting Mana. Every 3rd
    basic attack unleashes a "Chain Lightning" that jumps between 4 nearby enemies,
    dealing 10 + 10% ability power Magic Damage and applying hex status condition.
